    </section>
</nav></header><main aria-label="main content"><div class="speakable">
      <b data-is-speakable>Judge Gonzalo Curiel Attacked By Donald Trump For Mexican Heritage</b>   <b data-is-speakable>The likely GOP standard-bearer has accused the judge of bias in the Trump University fraud case because of his Mexican ancestry. But he's widely respected and took on a drug cartel under death threat.</b>
</div>
